claim.claim-text:
1. A sports cap having a crown and a visor extending outward from the bottom edge of the crown, wherein the visor comprises:
an intermediate support layer that maintains the visor in shape, the intermediate support layer having a top side, a bottom side, multiple recesses on the top side, a top layer covering the top side of the intermediate support layer;
a positioning block fitted into one recess of the intermediate support layer, the positioning block having a center insertion hole, a bottom layer covering the bottom side of the intermediate support layer opposite to the top layer;
a lining layer sandwiched between the intermediate support layer and the bottom layer; and
a hold down member fitted into one recess of the intermediate support layer to hold down the positioning block, the hold down member having a center through hole in axial alignment with the center insertion hole of the positioning block, a group of first mounting legs that secure the positioning block, and a group of second mounting legs fastened to an associating recess of the intermediate support layer.
